Package: nfsdiag
Version: 0.7.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libtirpc3
Suggests: nfs-common
Maintainer: Leandro Ferreira <leandrodsferreira@gmail.com>
Description: NFS diagnostic tool
 nfsdiag tests NFS servers from the client side.
 It checks network connectivity, rpcbind, NFS protocol versions,
 exports, permissions, UID/GID mapping, authentication, and performance.
